Here are a few things that I have made

Impulse Workout React Native Firebase Exercises API Expo CLI VS Code

------------

A collaborative app made for those looking to workout in groups. This app allows users to connect with their friends and share workouts that they create within the app itself.

This Website React Tailwind VS Code

------------

This very website has marked a leap in my knowledge in the field. Looking to finally put my name out there in a meaningful way, I created this website.

Rube Goldberg Project React p5.js VS Code

------------

A digital take on the popular Rube Goldberg challenge. Using a physics engine, I made a simple project that features gravity manipulation and other interesting factors.

Healthy Mates Nutrition Firebase Exercises API Android Studio

------------

A simple android based application I developed with my good friend. Made when we had little knowlege in android development, this nutrition companion serves as a product of our exploration.

Jeopardy React VS Code

------------

A simple one player jeopardy game that prompts the player with pre-generated addition questions. Made using simple react components, I used this project to familiarize myself with the framework.

Life Simulator IntelliJ IDEA

------------

A grid based simulation that features a simple ecosystem of rabbits, deer, cheetas, and a vast enviornment. Using conditionals, the program is able to simulate life within this small sample size.

Fighting RPG IntelliJ IDEA

------------

A Fighting game that showcased a live fighting mechanic. Using overlapping conditionals, I was able to mimic a sense of real time combat in this short, story driven RPG game.

This and more in my Github!{" "} Check it out
